7
00:01:23,799 --> 00:01:24,319
Could it be...

8
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:25,519
This...

9
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:25,879
That's enough.

10
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,079
Aunt Mu.

11
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,560
No matter what kind of misunderstanding is happening inside,

12
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,760
