20
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:55,000
Huiming.

21
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:55,840
What do you think?

22
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,000
Huiming.

23
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:01,959
Why are you here?

24
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:02,879
I'm not here.

25
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,480
Where did Aunt Lu think I was?

26
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,959
I wasn't feeling well just now.

27
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,759
I stepped out from the banquet to get some air.

28
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:10,479
Then...

29
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,800
Who's inside then?

30
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,400
The room key card is here.

31
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:29,840
Get out.

32
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,479
Why is it you?

33
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,439
Get out.

34
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:33,840
Get out of here!

35
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,879
Miss Liu, how can you act like this?

36
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,639
Just now, you clearly said

37
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,120
