38
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,080
Get out!

39
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:44,479
What nonsense are you talking about?

40
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:45,960
You're just a waiter.

41
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,439
How could my daughter possibly like you?

42
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:48,400
Someone, come!

43
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,439
Take him back to the Lu family for punishment.

44
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,360
Nobody move!

45
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:52,400
What's going on?

46
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,240
Is this matter just going to end like this?

47
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:58,080
You all thought the person inside was me just now.

48
00:02:58,439 --> 00:03:00,000
I have to give my fiancée an explanation.

49
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:02,400
Take him to the police station.

50
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,039
If we don't find out the truth,

51
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:05,039
I won't let this go.

52
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,280
Huiming

53
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:13,000
You grew up together with Yinyin.

54
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,719
You can't just stand by and watch her be humiliated.

55
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,759
If I had known it would turn out like this,

56
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:17,039
